<br>
In unrest you learn quick... if you don't wanna get trained, stay off the tracks.  You can sit on the back or side wall of the zone for hours hearing &quot;train&quot; being called and having no problems.  It's only ever people by the fountains or trying to pull out the front door that get trained and generally when I was there, if they complained, they got laughed at by the regulars.<br>
<br>
Had to be really awake zoning in.  Like if there are a bunch of panting bloodied people at 20% health siting on the DC side of the zone.. mebby ask around a bit before you zone in )<br>
<br>
I think I lived in unrest from maybe level 12 to... ?? whenever the mobs by fatty start to turn lite blue.  I think this zone has heard me shout DING more than any other.<br>
